# Google OAuth Credentials (required for Calendar sync)
# Setup steps:
#   1. Go to https://console.cloud.google.com/
#   2. Create a new project (or select existing)
#   3. Enable "Google Calendar API" in the API Library
#   4. Go to Credentials → Create Credentials → OAuth 2.0 Client ID
#   5. App type: Web Application
#   6. Add Authorized redirect URI: http://localhost:8000/auth/callback
#   7. Copy the Client ID and Client Secret below
